[
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hello. My name is Katherine Nepo. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm a program manager ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=11"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the App Store Trust and Safety team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=13"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this video, my colleague Jeremy Stober and I ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=16"
  },
  {
    "text": "will show you how to safeguard your ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "accounts, promotions, and content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today, we will discuss the importance of designing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "for trust and safety and present a suite of tools ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you can use to protect your apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "and your customers from attackers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=34"
  },
  {
    "text": "Jeremy will walk you through account risks ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=37"
  },
  {
    "text": "and promotion abuse. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "I will close by talking about content risks. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "The Apple platform is designed to help your business ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=46"
  },
  {
    "text": "grow and thrive with experiences that are trusted, safe, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "and fair for you and your customers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=55"
  },
  {
    "text": "We're going to review how Sign in with Apple ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=58"
  },
  {
    "text": "brings the simplicity and security ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=61"
  },
  {
    "text": "of two-factor authentication to your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "We will then learn how you can protect promotions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=67"
  },
  {
    "text": "and offers and defend the integrity of your ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=70"
  },
  {
    "text": "app with DeviceCheck and App Attest.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=73"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your features are exciting to your customers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "and may be attractive to attackers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=79"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app includes the ability to create ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=83"
  },
  {
    "text": "and manage accounts, supports user-generated content, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=85"
  },
  {
    "text": "offers promotional pricing, or includes premium content, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "it may be a target for fraud and abuse. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=93"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are many types of abuse that can happen ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "after you publish your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=100"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a closer look at three of them.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "In many app experiences, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "accounts are used to protect users' assets. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "Attackers, eager to gain access, seek new ways to take ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "over customer accounts and steal their data.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=116"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app offers promotions, you may be targeted by ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=121"
  },
  {
    "text": "attackers seeking to take advantage of your discounts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "or otherwise manipulate your app or server. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "These attackers can be opportunistic individuals ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=132"
  },
  {
    "text": "or large-scale operations. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=135"
  },
  {
    "text": "Attackers can scrape servers for valuable content and steal ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=138"
  },
  {
    "text": "legitimate apps to modify, repackage, and resell them ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=142"
  },
  {
    "text": "outside of the App Store, which can impact your business. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=147"
  },
  {
    "text": "I will now turn it over to Jeremy to talk about your ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=152"
  },
  {
    "text": "account risks and how you can protect your users. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=155"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you, Katherine. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll begin by talking about account risks ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you should be aware of as an app developer.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "Many apps and services require customers to create accounts. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=167"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, several problems can arise ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "from managing customer accounts. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=174"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, there is an incentive ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "for others to compromise the security of your ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "customers' valuable accounts. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=182"
  },
  {
    "text": "Accounts can be taken over through no fault of yours. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=184"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your users might be vulnerable to sophisticated ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "phishing attacks, have their passwords leaked ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=190"
  },
  {
    "text": "from unaffiliated services, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "or be the victim of misplaced trust. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "According to the Anti-phishing Working Group, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=200"
  },
  {
    "text": "an international consortium, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "the number of reported phishing attacks ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "observed by its members doubled over the course of 2020. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "Since user accounts are valuable, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=213"
  },
  {
    "text": "attackers may target them.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=215"
  },
  {
    "text": "In addition to account compromises, if you use customer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": "feedback in your app, for example, to power a ratings ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=222"
  },
  {
    "text": "or recommendation system, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "you may be creating a situation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=228"
  },
  {
    "text": "where that feedback can be used for illicit gain. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=230"
  },
  {
    "text": "This might incentivize ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "the creation of high volumes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=234"
  },
  {
    "text": "of fake accounts that are used ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "to manipulate these systems. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=239"
  },
  {
    "text": "Fake account creations can overload infrastructure, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "disrupt user experience, and impact the overall authenticity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=244"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the app experience you are working hard to craft.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=248"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are other forms of abuse that can arise ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=253"
  },
  {
    "text": "from inauthentic account creation. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, if users can communicate with each other, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "then there may be an incentive to send unsolicited advertising ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "over the platform you create using fake accounts. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=266"
  },
  {
    "text": "This can adversely impact the customer experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=271"
  },
  {
    "text": "and your reputation.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple offers a few tools that developers can use ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "to better manage account risks. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "One method to avoid a number of issues with account ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "management is to adopt Sign in with Apple. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "Integrating with Sign in with Apple will ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "allow you to benefit from Apple's robust ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "and ongoing efforts to keep customer accounts secure. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=292"
  },
  {
    "text": "Sign in with Apple is protected by Apple's ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=296"
  },
  {
    "text": "two-factor authentication. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "Customers on Apple devices can sign in ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=300"
  },
  {
    "text": "and re-authenticate with Face ID or Touch ID any time. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "The benefits to integrating with Sign in with Apple ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=308"
  },
  {
    "text": "are not limited to security. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "The credential return on first authorization includes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "a flag that indicates with a high degree confidence ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=316"
  },
  {
    "text": "that a user is real and not a bot.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": "This flag can be checked on the client. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=324"
  },
  {
    "text": "If a flag indicates a user is likely real, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=326"
  },
  {
    "text": "no additional challenge is needed. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=329"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, if the platform is unsupported, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=333"
  },
  {
    "text": "or the value returned is unknown, a challenge ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=336"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the user is recommended to prevent scripted traffic. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=339"
  },
  {
    "text": "To provide this flag, Apple uses a private, secure, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=343"
  },
  {
    "text": "on-device machine learning model in combination with ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "service side inferences based on account activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=351"
  },
  {
    "text": "With Sign in with Apple, you can take advantage ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=355"
  },
  {
    "text": "of Apple's world-class security ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "and industry-leading antifraud protections. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=359"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you are not using Sign in with Apple, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=363"
  },
  {
    "text": "there are a number of tools ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=366"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you can use to improve ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=367"
  },
  {
    "text": "account security and prevent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=369"
  },
  {
    "text": "inauthentic account creations. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=371"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are several videos describing ways ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=374"
  },
  {
    "text": "to encourage strong and unique passwords ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=377"
  },
  {
    "text": "without increasing user friction. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "Watch \"One tap account security upgrades\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=382"
  },
  {
    "text": "and \"Autofill everywhere\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "for more information.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=388"
  },
  {
    "text": "For inauthentic account creation, prevention means ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=391"
  },
  {
    "text": "making risk-based decisions using the data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=394"
  },
  {
    "text": "you are able to collect from the account creation request ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=397"
  },
  {
    "text": "like email domain and other account details ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=401"
  },
  {
    "text": "that may be part of your sign-up flow.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=404"
  },
  {
    "text": "As part of your strategy, you may want to limit the number ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=408"
  },
  {
    "text": "of account creations that can happen on a single Apple device. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=411"
  },
  {
    "text": "Limiting account creation on physical devices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=416"
  },
  {
    "text": "will make it more difficult ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=418"
  },
  {
    "text": "to create large numbers of fake accounts. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=420"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple offers an API called DeviceCheck ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "that can help with this. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=426"
  },
  {
    "text": "Using this API, you can effectively ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=428"
  },
  {
    "text": "limit account creations on authentic Apple devices. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=430"
  },
  {
    "text": "You may be promoting your business with free ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "or discounted items in your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=437"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, I'll talk about an example of how this can be abused.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=440"
  },
  {
    "text": "Suppose you want to offer an in-app promotion ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=445"
  },
  {
    "text": "to grow your business. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=448"
  },
  {
    "text": "Depending on the type of app, this could be anything ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=450"
  },
  {
    "text": "from a free sandwich to a discounted trial. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=452"
  },
  {
    "text": "You may find, however, that uptake of the special offer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=455"
  },
  {
    "text": "comes at a cost, as some people abuse the promotion ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=459"
  },
  {
    "text": "by re-downloading the app multiple times.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "Using the DeviceCheck API, you can ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=467"
  },
  {
    "text": "limit the number of promotion redemptions per device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=469"
  },
  {
    "text": "while protecting user privacy.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=473"
  },
  {
    "text": "The service allows you to set two bits of information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=477"
  },
  {
    "text": "on each device in a way that's strongly tied ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=479"
  },
  {
    "text": "to device authenticity and that can be read back ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=483"
  },
  {
    "text": "even after a complete reset of the device.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "At a high level, the use of DeviceCheck will allow you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=491"
  },
  {
    "text": "to verify that the device is real and allow you to query ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=494"
  },
  {
    "text": "previously set values of the two permitted bits. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=498"
  },
  {
    "text": "You have the ability to set and change the bits ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=503"
  },
  {
    "text": "as you please. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=506"
  },
  {
    "text": "In the case of a free promotion, you can use the value ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=508"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the return bits to determine if the device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=511"
  },
  {
    "text": "has been used to redeem the promotion in the past. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=514"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also choose to set the bits per device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=518"
  },
  {
    "text": "on account creation instead, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=521"
  },
  {
    "text": "which would offer a robust new signal ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=523"
  },
  {
    "text": "tied to verified hardware that you can use ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=526"
  },
  {
    "text": "in rate limiting account creation in your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=529"
  },
  {
    "text": "After a period of time, you can choose to reset the bits. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=534"
  },
  {
    "text": "This will facilitate reuse of the promotion ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=538"
  },
  {
    "text": "on a time period that you control and could help ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=541"
  },
  {
    "text": "manage situations where devices change hands.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=544"
  },
  {
    "text": "More details are available in the videos ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=549"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Privacy and your apps\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=551"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as the video “Mitigate fraud ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=553"
  },
  {
    "text": "with App Attest and DeviceCheck.” ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=556"
  },
  {
    "text": "Katherine will now talk about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=558"
  },
  {
    "text": "ways to protect your content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=560"
  },
  {
    "text": "and APIs from inauthentic clients. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=563"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you, Jeremy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=565"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's walk through some of the risks ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=567"
  },
  {
    "text": "potentially posed to your content.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=569"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your content is valuable ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=573"
  },
  {
    "text": "and may be an attractive target for attackers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=575"
  },
  {
    "text": "An attacker can develop and distribute ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=579"
  },
  {
    "text": "unauthorized software that allows unpermitted access ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=581"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your app's premium content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=585"
  },
  {
    "text": "This illicit access may negatively impact your earnings ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=588"
  },
  {
    "text": "and create opportunities for cheating and deception. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=592"
  },
  {
    "text": "Such abuses may undermine the trust of your users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=597"
  },
  {
    "text": "and ultimately harm your business.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=601"
  },
  {
    "text": "To help you protect the integrity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "of your app experiences, we created App Attest, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=606"
  },
  {
    "text": "which provides app protection ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=610"
  },
  {
    "text": "starting with iOS 14 and tvOS 15. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=612"
  },
  {
    "text": "App Attest enables you to verify ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=617"
  },
  {
    "text": "that the apps connecting to your servers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=620"
  },
  {
    "text": "are the apps that you published on the App Store, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=623"
  },
  {
    "text": "unmodified and running on genuine Apple devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=626"
  },
  {
    "text": "Leveraging Apple's secure enclave processor, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=632"
  },
  {
    "text": "iOS and tvOS generate a cryptographic attestation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=635"
  },
  {
    "text": "of your app's identity which you can send to your server ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=640"
  },
  {
    "text": "for verification before making your critical assets available. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=644"
  },
  {
    "text": "App Attest is easy to use. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=648"
  },
  {
    "text": "With only a few exchanges between your app and your server ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=650"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can verify the identity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=654"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the app requesting your content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=656"
  },
  {
    "text": "For more information on App Attest, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=659"
  },
  {
    "text": "including how your server ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=662"
  },
  {
    "text": "can perform verification, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=663"
  },
  {
    "text": "please check out the ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=665"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Mitigate fraud with App Attest and DeviceCheck\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=666"
  },
  {
    "text": "technical video.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=669"
  },
  {
    "text": "The tools we discussed today will enable you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=672"
  },
  {
    "text": "to guard your apps, your users, and your content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=675"
  },
  {
    "text": "Implement Sign in with Apple to secure your accounts from ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=679"
  },
  {
    "text": "attackers and prevent access to your valuable data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=682"
  },
  {
    "text": "Use DeviceCheck to prevent abuse of your promotional offerings. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=686"
  },
  {
    "text": "And protect your content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=691"
  },
  {
    "text": "with App Attest by validating ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=693"
  },
  {
    "text": "the authenticity of the apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=695"
  },
  {
    "text": "connecting to your server ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=697"
  },
  {
    "text": "before serving their requests. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=699"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you for watching. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=701"
  },
  {
    "text": "We look forward to seeing your businesses grow ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=703"
  },
  {
    "text": "and thrive in a fair, safe, and trusted environment. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=705"
  },
  {
    "text": "[percussive music]",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10110/?time=710"
  }
]